ğŸ” What Are Extended Regular Expressions?
Extended regex lets you write powerful search patterns without escaping everything.

âœ… Easier syntax
âœ… Cleaner expressions
âœ… More powerful pattern matching

ğŸ†š Basic vs Extended Regex
Feature	Basic Regex (grep)	Extended Regex (grep -E or egrep)
+, ?, {}	Need to escape with \	Used as-is
Cleaner syntax	âŒ No	âœ… Yes
Easier for complex patterns	âŒ	âœ…

