[a-z]+ â†’ one or more lowercase letters

[0-9]? â†’ optional digit at the end

ğŸ§  Subexpressions (Group + Repeat)
8ï¸âƒ£ Match: Multiple dev devices like /dev/t0p0, /dev/sda1
bash
Copy
Edit
egrep '/dev/[a-z]+[0-9]?([a-z]+[0-9]?)*' file.txt
Group: ([a-z]+[0-9]?)

Repeat that group 0 or more times: *

ğŸš« Negative Matching with Sets
